README
======

ffmpeg
------
use install.sh to install ffmpeg the first time

timelapse
---------
use flimeo.sh to create your timelapses (tested with a GoPro and a Pentax-K30 as source)


Testing
=======

To speed up testing use a custom url for ffmpeg download

  FFMPEG_BINARY_URL=http://0.0.0.0:8000/ffmpeg.tar.gz

Also serve the previousley downloaded file localy.

With Python

- 2.7: $ python2.7 -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000
- 3.x: $ python -m http.server 8000